</P>
<P>
Game 2: Oakland 6, Toronto 3 
</P>
<P>
Game 3: Toronto 7, Oakland 3 
</P>
<P>
Game 4: Oakland 6, Toronto 5 
</P>
<P>
Game 5: Oakland 4, Toronto 3 
</P>
<P>
Oakland wins series, 4-1 
</P>
<P>
