<P>
FIRE SAFETY -- State Fire Marshal can use late charges in licensing and listing 
programs. 
</P>
<P>
LAB FEES -- Permits the state Fire Marshal to charge for inspecting 
laboratories that test consumer products for fire safety. 
</P>
